	</ul>
	<p>The program ensures that your transactions are secure in two ways:</p>
	<h3>Encryption</h3>
	<p>This electronically scrambles the data stream between your computer and the program’s server. Encryption minimizes the risk that internet hackers and other users will alter or view information being transmitted. You must be using a browser with 128-bit encryption to access this website.</p>
	<h3>Firewalls</h3>
	<p>These are a combination of hardware and software designed to securely separate the outside world from the program’s internal computer systems and database.</p>
